Package: eog-annotation-plugin
Version: 1.0.0-1
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Jan Sechovec <jan@flexer.cz>
Installed-Size: 94
Depends: eog, python3-gi, python3-gi-cairo, gir1.2-gtk-3.0, gir1.2-rsvg-2.0
Section: graphics
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://flexer.cz
Description: Image annotation plugin for Eye of GNOME (EOG)
 A native plugin for GNOME Image Viewer (Eye of GNOME / EOG) that provides
 comprehensive annotation tools for images including:
 .
  * Arrows with multiple styles (Standard, Open, Double, Small, Large)
  * Numbered counter dots for step-by-step annotations
  * Rectangle and circle drawing tools
  * Text labels with formatting options (bold, italic, size)
  * Color selection and line width control
  * Unlimited undo/redo history
  * Copy to clipboard and save annotated images
  * Auto-hide toolbar when zoomed or in fullscreen mode
 .
 This plugin integrates seamlessly into EOG's interface and provides all
 tools in a compact, icon-based toolbar.
